commits.message:
Tooltip and typings

Moved tooltip HTML into Tooltip.svelte.

Adjusted some typings to be more general use.

More tooltip features

Added tooltip item icons.
Added DPS & Base Armor numbers.
Added tooltip item name.
Added item quality.
Added item slot
Added tooltip selection functionality.

Fixed build selection bug

Fixed a bug where selecting a previously selected build caused a major error.

Fixed build selector indexing bug

Fixed a bug where the previous build selections value would carry into the new build selection, sometimes causing an out of bounds error on the builds profile array.

Moved the build selection drop down from GearContainer.svelte into BuildSelector.svelte.
